<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 2 - Por qué estar en redes sociales</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .reason-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .reason-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 8px; background-color: #C0504D; z-index: 20;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 40px; left: 48px; width: 32px; height: 4px; background-color: #C0504D;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 90px; width: 300px; height: 20px;">
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #9CA3AF; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0;">Contexto</p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 60px; left: 48px; width: 860px; height: 42px;">
<h2 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0; line-height: 1.05;">Por qué tu negocio necesita estar en redes sociales</h2>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 50px; right: 48px; width: 100px; height: 50px; text-align: right;">
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #E5E7EB; margin: 0;">02</p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 120px; left: 48px; width: 840px; height: 40px;">
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">Más allá de una tendencia, es el canal principal donde tus clientes viven, interactúan y deciden.</p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; right: 0; top: 100px; width: 300px; height: 300px; background-color: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.5; z-index: 1;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; left: 40px; bottom: 40px; width: 150px; height: 150px; background-color: #EFF6FF; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.5; z-index: 1;"></div>
<div class="reason-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 180px; left: 48px; width: 290px; height: 240px; background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); z-index: 10;">
<div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">📢</div>
<h3 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">Visibilidad masiva</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
                Más de <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">5.240 millones</span> de personas usan redes sociales en 2025 (<span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">65%</span> de la población mundial).
            </p>
</div>
<div class="reason-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 180px; left: 366px; width: 290px; height: 240px; background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); z-index: 10;">
<div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">🎯</div>
<h3 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">Generación de leads</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
                El <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">56%</span> de las empresas obtiene clientes potenciales directamente desde redes sociales.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="reason-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 180px; left: 684px; width: 290px; height: 240px; background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); z-index: 10;">
<div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">💬</div>
<h3 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">Atención al cliente</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
                Más del <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">50%</span> de los consumidores prefiere resolver dudas con marcas a través de redes sociales.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="reason-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 450px; left: 48px; width: 450px; height: 240px; background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); z-index: 10; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
<div style="font-size: 48px; margin-right: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;">🛒</div>
<div>
<h3 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">Canal de ventas directo</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
                    El social commerce representa el <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">17%</span> de todas las ventas online en 2025. Un canal de venta directa sin intermediarios.
                </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="reason-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 450px; left: 524px; width: 450px; height: 240px; background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); z-index: 10; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
<div style="font-size: 48px; margin-right: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;">🏛️</div>
<div>
<h3 style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">No solo negocios</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
                    ONGs, instituciones educativas, artistas, profesionales y entidades públicas también se benefician. Es para <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #C0504D;">cualquier entidad</span> que quiera comunicar.
                </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-2" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">3 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-4" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


